        ["1354"] = "A rib of skeleton from ruins. Take this to Samed in the town of Gludio.",
        ["1355"] = "A spine of skeleton from ruins. Take this to Samed in the town of Gludio.",
        ["1356"] = "An arm bone of skeleton from ruins. Take this to Samed in the town of Gludio.",
        ["1357"] = "A thigh bone of skeleton from ruins. Take this to Samed in the town of Gludio.",
        ["1358"] = "A complete skeleton put together with bone pieces by undertaker Varsak. Take this to Samed in the town of Gludio.",
        ["1359"] = "A soldier badge of foreign troops. Take this to Leopold in Gludin.",
        ["1360"] = "A badge of high ranking of Gracian foreign troops. Take this to Leopold in Gludin.",
        ["1361"] = "A badge of captain ranking of Gracian foreign troops. Take this to Leopold in Gludin.",
        ["1362"] = "The hard carapace of a spider. Often used to coat a shield or a helmet. Take this to Trader Arodin.",
        ["1363"] = "Tough, stretchy spider web. Used to make bowstrings. Take this to Trader Arodin.",
        ["1364"] = "A sac with a spider's deadly poison in it. Can be sold to Trader Cullinas in Gludin.",
