        ["1366"] = "The transparent part of monster eye. Take this to Trader Sarien.",
        ["1367"] = "Collect 50 wolf claws and take them to Trader Payne of the weapons and armor shop.",
        ["1368"] = "The metal shackles attached around the neck of the imp race. Take this to Sentry Kristin.",
        ["1369"] = "The mark that indicates one is a member of the Black Lion troop.",
