        ["1562"] = "These dice were specially made for gambling. Take these to Blacksmith Brunon.",
        ["1563"] = "This contract says if Brunon gets the 20 stolen jewels back from goblins, he can get the star diamond back.",
        ["1564"] = "This jewel is obtained by the goblin brigand leader. Take 10 aquamarines and 10 chrysoberyls to Blacksmith Brunon.",
