        ["1624"] = "A charm with inscription of flame mantra. Take this and gather grizzly blood and take to Seer Umos.",
        ["1625"] = "A glass bottle filled with grizzly blood. Gather 3 and take to Seer Umos.",
        ["1626"] = "A cauldron filled with grizzly blood. Take this to the Duda-Mara totem spirit.",
        ["1627"] = "A net made with Spirit's Spider Silk. Use this to capture Durka Spirit hidden inside Venomous Spiders.",
        ["1628"] = "Durka spirit bound inside Spirit Net. Take this to the Duda-Mara totem spirit.",
        ["1629"] = "An evil parasite spirit that comes out from spiders contaminated with the evil durka spirit. It is the key for calling upon the evil durka spirit.",
        ["1630"] = "Blood spilt by the Duda-Mara totem spirit. Take this and go to Seer Umos.",
        ["1631"] = "A token that shows one has the qualifications to become an Orc Shaman. Take this to the high prefect, to change your occupation to an Orc Shaman.",
        ["1632"] = "A ring given to artisan aspirants by Blacksmith Silvera. Strike down the boogle ratman gang and collect their front teeth.",
        ["1633"] = "The certificate for passing the 1st artisan test. To take the next test, you must go to Blacksmith Kluto of the village Gludin.",
        ["1634"] = "The certificate for passing the 2nd artisan test. Take this and go to Blacksmith Kluto in Gludin.",
        ["1635"] = "The certificate for passing the final Artisan test. Take this to the head blacksmith to change occupations to an Artisan.",
        ["1636"] = "The ugly front bucktooth of a boogle ratman. Just looking at it will make you nauseous. Collect 10 of these and take them to Blacksmith Silvera.",
        ["1637"] = "The boogle ratman leader's big tooth. Before its stink makes you pass out, collect 2 of them and take them to Blacksmith Silvera.",
        ["1638"] = "Blacksmith Kluto's letter. Take to Blacksmith Pinter in the Town of Gludio.",
        ["1639"] = "Trace left by thieves. Kill Vuku Orc fighters, recover stolen items and take them to Blacksmith Pinter.",
        ["1640"] = "A secret box stolen by Vuku orc fighters. The contents of the box are unknown, but anyway, take it to Blacksmith Pinter.",
        ["1641"] = "A secret box received from Pinter. The contents are unknown, but do not worry and take it to Blacksmith Kluto in the Village of Gludin.",
        ["1642"] = "A mark certifying that one has earned the right to become a Scavenger. If you take it to a Warehouse Chief, you can transfer your class to Scavenger.",
