        ["2701"] = "Creta's letter describing the theft of the Scriptures of Knowledge. Take this to Magister Dieter in the Town of Giran.",
        ["2702"] = "A letter from Magister Dieter to Trader Edroc of the weapons shop of Hunters Village.",
