        ["2747"] = "A proof obtained from Actea of Verdant Wilds. Deliver this, along with the breath of winds, to Hierarch Asterios.",
        ["2748"] = "Deliver this to Magister Clayton, member of the Dark Elf Guild, in the Town of Dion.",
