        ["3119"] = "A mark given to those who have passed the Trial of the Guildsman. An occupation change related item.",
        ["3120"] = "A recommendation letter written by Warehouse Keeper Valkon. Take this and go to Blacksmith Altran of Talking Island.",
        ["3121"] = "The fruit of mandragoras, known for their uses in treating ailments.",
        ["3122"] = "Blacksmith Altran's instructions. The instructions are to gather materials and create 7 journeyman's rings.",
        ["3123"] = "A recommendation letter written by Blacksmith Altran. Take this and go to Warehouse Keeper Norman of the Village of Gludin.",
        ["3124"] = "A recommendation letter written by Blacksmith Altran. Take this and go to Blacksmith Pinter of the Town of Gludio.",
        ["3125"] = "Warehouse Keeper Norman's instructions. The instructions are to go to Blacksmith Duning of Hunters Village and bring back the key.",
        ["3126"] = "Warehouse Keeper Norman's receipt. Take this and go to Blacksmith Duning of the Hunters Village.",
        ["3127"] = "Blacksmith Duning's instructions. It gives an order to recover 30 keys from Breka orcs.",
        ["3128"] = "Mithril key recovered from Breka orcs. Collect 30 and take them to Blacksmith Duning.",
        ["3129"] = "Ingredient list of Warehouse Keeper Norman: 70 units of gray bone powder, 70 granite whetstones, 70 units of red pigment, and 70 units of braided yarn.",
        ["3130"] = "The powder collected from the bones of ghouls and strains. Gather 70 of these and take them to Warehouse Keeper Norman.",
        ["3131"] = "A whetstone made from the fragments of the granite golem. Gather 70 of these and take them to Warehouse Keeper Norman.",
        ["3132"] = "Red pigment obtained by slaying the dead seeker bat. Gather 70 of these and take them to Warehouse Keeper Norman.",
        ["3133"] = "Braided yarn obtained by slaying the silenos. Gather 70 of these and take them to Warehouse Keeper Norman.",
        ["3134"] = "A material used to make the journeyman's ring.",
        ["3135"] = "Instructions of Blacksmith Pinter: Find and bring back 70 amber beads.",
        ["3136"] = "A bead-shaped piece of amber. Collect 70 of these and take them to Blacksmith Pinter.",
        ["3137"] = "An unrefined lump of amber. The material used in creating the Amber Bead.",
        ["3138"] = "Ingredient item used to make a journeyman's ring.",
        ["3139"] = "To pass the Trial of the Guildsman, you must create 7 of these rings. Take the completed rings to Warehouse Keeper Valkon.",
        ["3140"] = "A mark given to those who have passed the Testimony of Life. An occupation change related item.",
        ["3141"] = "Letter by Master Cardien. Take this and go to Hierarch Asterios of the Elven Village.",
        ["3142"] = "A talisman given by Hierarch Asterios. Take this and return to Master Cardien in the Town of Dion.",
        ["3143"] = "A letter given by Hierarch Asterios. Take this and go to Thalia, who lives on the eastern shores of Iris Lake.",
        ["3144"] = "The charm given by Hierarch Asterios to keep in possession while searching for the water of life.",
        ["3145"] = "A diagram of the grail, given by Thalia. Take this and go to Blacksmith Pushkin of Town of Giran.",
        ["3146"] = "Thalia's letter. Take this and go to Arkenia, who is at the Altar of Rites.",
        ["3147"] = "Thalia's letter. Take this and go to Isael Silvershadow of the Hunters Village.",
        ["3148"] = "A letter containing Thalia's instructions. The instructions are to come back after reaching level 38.",
        ["3149"] = "A list given by Blacksmith Pushkin. \"10 pure Mithril Ore, 20 ant soldier acid, 20 Wyrm talons\"",
        ["3150"] = "A cup crafted by Blacksmith Pushkin that is made of pure mithril. Take this back to Thalia.",
        ["3151"] = "A contract written by Arkenia. The contract states that she will give stardust in return for Andariel's book from the Village of Gludin.",
        ["3152"] = "Arkenia's instructions. The instructions are to bring back Andariel's book from the Temple of Einhasad in the Village of Gludin.",
        ["3153"] = "A list given by Priest Adonius: 20 spider ichor and 20 harpy's down.",
        ["3154"] = "A copy of Andariel's book given by Priest Adonius. Take this back to Arkenia.",
        ["3155"] = "The silver dust received from Arkenia of the Dark Elves. Take this back to Thalia.",
        ["3156"] = "A document containing Isael Silvershadow's instructions. It asks you to recover 6 pieces of talins spear from Leto lizardman shamans.",
        ["3157"] = "A letter given by Isael Silvershadow. Take this back to Thalia along with Talin's spear.",
        ["3158"] = "A grail crafted of pure mithril. Catch the tears of the unicorn with the grail and take it back to Thalia.",
        ["3159"] = "The tears shed by Eva's unicorn when it is killed with Talin's spear. Take this back to Thalia.",
        ["3160"] = "The holy water that contains the powers of life to rejuvenate the Mother Tree. Take this and go to Hierarch Asterios.",
        ["3161"] = "The ore of pure mithril. Gather 10 of these, along with the rest of the ingredients, and take them back to Blacksmith Pushkin.",
        ["3162"] = "The acid collected from ant soldiers after slaying them. Gather 20 bottles of this, along with the rest of the ingredients, and take them back to Blacksmith Pushkin.",
        ["3163"] = "The talon of a Wyrm obtained after slaying it. Gather 20 of these, along with the rest of the ingredients, and take them back to Blacksmith Pushkin.",
        ["3164"] = "The ichor of a marsh spider. Gather 20 units of this and take them back to Priest Adonius.",
        ["3165"] = "The down feathers obtained after slaying a harpy. Gather 20 of these and take them back to Priest Adonius.",
        ["3166"] = "The blade portion of Talin's spear. Take this, along with the remaining portions of the spear, back to Isael Silvershadow.",
        ["3167"] = "The shaft portion of Talin's spear. Take this, along with the remaining portions of the spear, back to Isael Silvershadow.",
        ["3168"] = "A decorative jewel that adorned Talin's spear. Take this, along with the remaining portions of the spear, back to Isael Silvershadow.",
        ["3169"] = "A decorative jewel that adorned Talin's spear. Take this, along with the remaining portions of the spear, back to Isael Silvershadow.",
        ["3170"] = "A decorative jewel that adorned Talin's spear. Take this, along with the remaining portions of the spear, back to Isael Silvershadow.",
        ["3171"] = "A decorative jewel that adorned Talin's spear. Take this, along with the remaining portions of the spear, back to Isael Silvershadow.",
        ["3172"] = "A mark given to those who have passed the Testimony of Fate. An item for occupational change.",
        ["3173"] = "A letter sent by Magister Kaira to Brother Metheus of the Temple of Einhasad. This must be delivered secretly.",
        ["3174"] = "A jar for storing the remains of the dead. Take this to the Execution Grounds and search for the remains of Metheus's sister.",
        ["3175"] = "The remains of Kasandra, Metheus's sister. Take this back to Brother Metheus.",
        ["3176"] = "A textbook of various herbs and their usages. It also contains information about the deadly poison belladonna.",
        ["3177"] = "10 units each of medusa's blood, marsh spider fluids, dead seeker's dung, tyrant's blood and nightshade root.",
        ["3178"] = "The bottled blood of a medusa. Collect 10 of these and take them back to Master Ixia",
        ["3179"] = "The bottled fluids of a marsh spider. Collect 10 of these and take them back to Master Ixia.",
        ["3180"] = "The dung of dead seeker bats. Collect 10 of these and take them back to Master Ixia.",
        ["3181"] = "The bottled blood of tyrant. Collect 10 of these and take them back to Master Ixia.",
        ["3182"] = "The roots of the rare nightshade herb. Collect 10 of these and take them back to Master Ixia.",
        ["3183"] = "A legendary poison that can kill a bull with a single drop. Take this to Brother Metheus.",
        ["3184"] = "The skull of Alders, who drafted the copy of Kaysha's Revelations. Take this to Magister Kaira.",
        ["3185"] = "Skull of Priest Alders. Take it to Magister Roa, a distant descendant of the priest.",
        ["3186"] = "The receipt for the item that Alder entrusted to the warehouse. Take this and go to the warehouse in the Village of Gludin.",
        ["3187"] = "A copy of Kaysha's Revelations. Take this to Magister Kaira.",
        ["3188"] = "A note where Magister Kaira's instructions are written. The instructions are to come back after reaching level 38.",
        ["3189"] = "A recommendation letter written by Magister Kaira. Take this and go to Tetrarch Thifiell of the Dark Elven Village.",
        ["3190"] = "A charm given by Tetrarch Thifiell to keep in possession until the Initiation Ceremony of the Shillien Circle is complete.",
        ["3191"] = "A letter from Tetrarch Thifiell to Arkenia. Arkenia is at the Dark Elven Initiation Altar.",
        ["3192"] = "A note written by Arkenia. It contains instructions to bring back red fairy dust and blight treant sap.",
        ["3193"] = "A garnet given by the Bloody Pixy as a token of promise. Bring one skull each of four different races.",
        ["3194"] = "The skull of Grandis. Bring this to the Bloody Pixy.",
        ["3195"] = "The skull of Karul Bugbear. Bring this to the Bloody Pixy.",
        ["3196"] = "The skull of a Breka Overlord. Bring this to the Bloody Pixy.",
        ["3197"] = "The skull of a Leto Lizardman Overlord. Bring this to the Bloody Pixy.",
        ["3198"] = "Red fairy dust given by the bloody pixy. Take this to Arkenia.",
        ["3199"] = "A seed given by a blight treant as a mark of promise. Slay the black willow lurker and bring back its leaf.",
        ["3200"] = "A leaf obtained by slaying the black willow lurker. Take this to the Blight Treant.",
        ["3201"] = "The sap of a blight treant. Take this to Arkenia.",
        ["3202"] = "A letter written by Arkenia. It states that the Initiation Ceremony of the Shillien Circle is complete. Take this to Tetrarch Thifiell.",
        ["3203"] = "A mark given to those who have passed the Testimony of Glory. An item for occupational change.",
        ["3204"] = "Collect and return with 10 manashen shards, 10 tyrant talons and 10 guardian basilisk fangs.",
        ["3205"] = "A shard of the broken manashen. Collect 10 and take them back to Prefect Vokian.",
        ["3206"] = "The talons plucked from a slain Tyrant. Collect 10 and take them back to Prefect Vokian.",
        ["3207"] = "The fangs of a slain guardian basilisk. Collect 10 and take them back to Prefect Vokian.",
        ["3208"] = "Prefect Vokian's orders. The instructions are to go and seek out the Gandi Chief Chianta in the Town of Dion.",
        ["3209"] = "A symbol given to those representing Pa'agrio Lord Kakai.",
        ["3210"] = "Orders of Gandi Chief Chianta. The instructions are to go and recover the flame scepter from the lower orc tribes.",
        ["3211"] = "Scepter of flame which can be obtained from a Breka orc chief. Take it along with 4 other tribes' scepters and go see Gandi Chief Chianta.",
        ["3212"] = "The flame scepter received from the Enku orc chief. Take this, along with the remaining 4 scepters, to Gandi Chief Chianta.",
        ["3213"] = "The flame scepter received from the Vuku orc chief. Take this, along with the remaining 4 scepters, to Gandi Chief Chianta.",
        ["3214"] = "The flame scepter received from the Turek orc chief. Take this, along with the remaining 4 scepters, to Gandi Chief Chianta.",
        ["3215"] = "The flame scepter received from the Lennunt orc chief. Take this, along with the remaining 4 scepters, to Gandi Chief Chianta.",
        ["3216"] = "Gandi Chief Chianta's orders. The instructions are to come back for further orders after reaching level 38.",
        ["3217"] = "Gandi Chief Chianta's orders. The instructions are to bring back 20 each of Timak and Tamlin orc heads.",
        ["3218"] = "The head of a Tamlin orc cut off after being slain. Collect 20 of these and take them to Gandi Chief Chianta.",
        ["3219"] = "The head of a Timak orc, cut off after being slain. Collect 20 of these and take them to Gandi Chief Chianta.",
        ["3220"] = "A box containing the 5 flame scepters recovered from the lesser orc tribes. Take this to Seer Tanapi of the Orc Village.",
        ["3221"] = "Kill Pashika, son of Voltar, cut his head off and show it to Breka Chief Voltar.",
        ["3222"] = "Kill Vultus, son of Voltar, cut his head off and show it to Breka Chief Voltar.",
        ["3223"] = "Glove that was thrown out by Breka Chief Voltar. Slay Pashika and Vultus, sons of Voltar.",
        ["3224"] = "The head of an Enku overlord, cut off after being slain. Show this to Enku Chief Kepra.",
        ["3225"] = "The glove thrown down by Enku Chief Kepra. Go and slay the Enku overlords.",
        ["3226"] = "The head of a Makum bugbear warrior, cut off after being slain. Show this to Turek Chief Burai.",
        ["3227"] = "The glove thrown down by Turek Chief Burai. Go and slay the Makum bugbear warriors.",
        ["3228"] = "Letter of Seer Manakia. Take it to Breka orc chief.",
        ["3229"] = "Seer Manakia's letter. Take this and go to the Enku Orc Chief.",
        ["3230"] = "Prefect Kasman's letter. Take this and go to the Vuku Orc Chief.",
        ["3231"] = "Prefect Kasman's letter. Take this and go to the Turek Orc Chief.",
        ["3232"] = "Prefect Kasman's letter. Take this and go to the Lennunt Orc Chief.",
        ["3233"] = "Vuku Chief Driko's contract. The contract contains instructions to hunt the marsh stakato drones in the Cruma Marshlands.",
        ["3234"] = "The husks of a marsh stakato drone. Collect 30 of these and take them to Vuku Chief Driko.",
        ["3235"] = "Seer Tanapi's orders. Hunt the Ragna Orc Chief and seers and recover the scepter of Tantosc.",
        ["3236"] = "The flame scepter of the now-perished Tantos tribe. Take this to Seer Tanapi.",
        ["3237"] = "A box containing the scepters recovered from the Orcs of the Tantos tribe. Take this to Pa'agrio Lord Kakai.",
        ["3238"] = "A mark given to those who have passed the Testimony of Prosperity. An occupation change related item.",
        ["3239"] = "A ring given to those Dwarves attempting the Testimony of Prosperity. Find the 4 proofs of prosperity.",
        ["3240"] = "A ring given to those Dwarves attempting the Testimony of Prosperity. Find Maphr's tablet, which contains the ultimate secrets of geometry.",
        ["3241"] = "Iron Gate Lockirin's account book. The proof of wealth. Take this to Warehouse Keeper Parman of Town of Giran.",
        ["3242"] = "A seed containing the blessings of Maphr. The proof of fertile lands. Take this to Warehouse Keeper Parman of Town of Giran.",
        ["3243"] = "A recipe good for childbirth and childbirth recovery. The proof of fertility. Take this to Warehouse Keeper Parman of Town of Giran.",
        ["3244"] = "Food regarded as the secret to the Elves' longevity. The proof of health. Take this to Warehouse Keeper Parman of Town of Giran.",
        ["3245"] = "A fragment of Maphr's tablet, which contains the ultimate secrets of geometry. Take this to Warehouse Keeper Parman of Town of Giran.",
        ["3246"] = "A license that allows the bearer to collect guild contributions. Seek out those who still owe contributions and collect the funds from them.",
        ["3247"] = "A notice that guild contributions are due. Take this to Golden Wheel's Spiron.",
        ["3248"] = "A notice that guild contributions are due. Take this to Silver Scale's Balanki.",
        ["3249"] = "A notice that guild contributions are due. Take this to Bronze Key's Keef.",
        ["3250"] = "A notice that guild contributions are due. Take this to Filaur of the Gray Pillar.",
        ["3251"] = "A notice that guild contributions are due. Take this to Black Anvil's Arin.",
        ["3252"] = "Trader Shari's guild contribution. Take this to Golden Wheel's Spiron.",
        ["3253"] = "Trader Mion's guild contribution. Take this to Silver Scale's Balanki.",
        ["3254"] = "Maryse Redbonnet's guild contribution. Take this to Silver Scale's Balanki.",
        ["3255"] = "Note containing Maryse Redbonnet's request that you bring back 10 leather hides for use in crafting items.",
        ["3256"] = "Master Toma's guild contribution. Take this to Black Anvil's Arin.",
        ["3257"] = "Miner Bolter's contribution receipt. Take this to Black Anvil's Arin to confirm if Miner Bolter has already submitted his contribution.",
        ["3258"] = "The contribution receipt received from Golden Wheel's Spiron. Collect 5 receipts and take them to Lockirin of the Iron Gate.",
        ["3259"] = "The contribution receipt received from Silver Scale's Balanki. Collect 5 receipts and take them to Lockirin of the Iron Gate.",
        ["3260"] = "The contribution receipt received from Bronze Key's Keef. Collect 5 receipts and take them to Lockirin of the Iron Gate.",
        ["3261"] = "A contribution receipt received from Filaur of the Gray Pillar. Collect 5 receipts and take them to Lockirin of the Iron Gate.",
        ["3262"] = "The contribution receipt received from Black Anvil's Arin. Collect 5 receipts and take them to Lockirin of the Iron Gate.",
        ["3263"] = "The bearer of this procuration hereby agrees to make contributions on behalf of Torocco. Take this to Bronze Key's Keef.",
        ["3264"] = "A list of ingredients that Guard Bright has written. \"20 mandragora petals, 10 bunches of crimson moss\"",
        ["3265"] = "The petals of a mandragora flower. Collect 20 of these and take them to Guard Bright.",
        ["3266"] = "Crimson Moss obtained from giant red ants. Collect 10 of these and take them to Guard Bright.",
        ["3267"] = "A flower bouquet made of mandragora petals and crimson moss. Take this to Emily in the Town of Dion.",
        ["3268"] = "A note containing Warehouse Keeper Parman's instructions. The instructions are to come back after reaching level 38.",
        ["3269"] = "Warehouse Keeper Parman's letter. Take this to Maestro Nikola of the Cruma Tower.",
        ["3270"] = "A piece of clay that Maestro Nikola has given. Use this to make a copy of the keyhole from the titan's box.",
        ["3271"] = "The keyhole pattern made from clay dough. Take this to Maestro Nikola.",
        ["3272"] = "20 stakato shells, 10 toad lord sacs, 10 spider thorns and 10 D-grade crystals.",
        ["3273"] = "The shell of a marsh stakato. A key ingredient in making the titan's key.",
        ["3274"] = "The Giant Spider's Poison Sac removed from the neck of a toad lord. A key ingredient in making the titan's key.",
        ["3275"] = "A thorn removed from the shell of a Marsh Spider. A key ingredient in making the Titan's Key.",
        ["3276"] = "A mark given to those who have passed the Test of the Champion. An item for occupational change.",
        ["3277"] = "Veteran Ascalon's letter. Take this to Mason in the Town of Dion.",
        ["3278"] = "A letter from Mason to Veteran Ascalon of Town of Giran.",
        ["3279"] = "A ring given by Mason. The ring is engraved with the symbol of the iron rose. Complete the revenge in place of Mason.",
        ["3280"] = "Veteran Ascalon's letter. Take this to Trader Groot of Town of Giran.",
        ["3281"] = "An insignia given by Trader Groot. It was formerly worn by the medics of the iron rose. Aid Trader Groot in his material gathering.",
        ["3282"] = "A letter from Trader Groot to Veteran Ascalon in Town of Giran.",
        ["3283"] = "Veteran Ascalon's letter. Take this to Captain Mouen of the Town of Oren.",
        ["3284"] = "Cut off and bring back the heads of 100 road scavengers or road collectors.",
        ["3285"] = "Destroy the Leto lizardmen and bring back 100 of their fangs.",
        ["3286"] = "A letter from Captain Mouen to Veteran Ascalon of Town of Giran.",
        ["3287"] = "An egg obtained after slaying a harpy. Collect 30 of these and take them to Trader Groot of Town of Giran.",
        ["3288"] = "The venom obtained after slaying a medusa. Collect 30 of these and take them to Trader Groot of Town of Giran.",
        ["3289"] = "The bile obtained after slaying a Windsus. Collect 30 of these and take them to Trader Groot of Town of Giran.",
        ["3290"] = "The head of a Bloody Axe Elite. Collect 10 of these and return to Mason in the Town of Dion.",
        ["3291"] = "The severed head of a road scavenger or road collector. Collect 10 of them and take them to Captain Mouen.",
        ["3292"] = "A fang from a slain Leto lizardman. Collect 10 of these and take them to Captain Mouen.",
        ["3293"] = "A mark given to those who have passed the Test of the Sagittarius. An occupation change related item.",
        ["3294"] = "Take this letter and go to Sagittarius Hamil of the Village of Floran.",
        ["3295"] = "Take this letter and meet with Sir Aron Tanford of the Southern Wastelands.",
        ["3296"] = "Take this letter and go to Prefect Vokian of Town of Giran.",
        ["3297"] = "Take this letter and go to Gauen of the Ivory Tower.",
        ["3298"] = "A stone engraved with a hunter's rune. Collect 10 of these and take them to Hamil of the Village of Floran.",
        ["3299"] = "A rune obtained from Breka orc overlords or Shamans. Collect 10 of these and take them, along with the snake talisman, to Prefect Vokian.",
        ["3300"] = "A strange talisman obtained after slaying Kadesh. Take this to Sagittarius Hamil of the Village of Floran.",
        ["3301"] = "Talisman that is related to a serpent totem spirit worshipped by Breka orcs. Take it to Prefect Vokian of Town of Giran.",
        ["3302"] = "A key ingredient in restoring the Crescent Bow. Take this, along with the rest of the ingredients, to Magister Gauen of the Ivory Tower.",
        ["3303"] = "A key ingredient in restoring the Crescent Bow. Take this, along with the rest of the ingredients, to Magister Gauen of the Ivory Tower.",
        ["3304"] = "A key ingredient in restoring the Crescent Bow. Take this, along with the rest of the ingredients, to Magister Gauen of the Ivory Tower.",
        ["3305"] = "A key ingredient in restoring the Crescent Bow. Take this, along with the rest of the ingredients, to Magister Gauen of the Ivory Tower.",
        ["3306"] = "The blood shed by Leto Lizardmen. Kadesh appears when enough of this is gathered.",
        ["3307"] = "A mark given to those who have passed the Test of Witchcraft. An occupation change related item.",
        ["3308"] = "A diagram of relics, given by Orim of the Shadow. The 6 jewels needed for opening the Cube of Aklantoth are depicted here.",
        ["3309"] = "A book that contains records on who purchased Aklantoth's Gems. \"Magister Iker, Magister Kaira, Trader Lara\"",
        ["3310"] = "Collect and bring back 20 dire Wyrm fangs, 20 Leto lizardman charms, and 20 enchanted stone golem heartstones.",
        ["3311"] = "The fangs of a slain Dire Wyrm. Collect 20 of these and take them to Magister Iker.",
