        ["3313"] = "A crystal found amongst the shattered fragments of an enchanted stone golem. Collect 20 of these and take them to Magister Iker.",
        ["3314"] = "Trader Lara's sales records. It is recorded that a man named Ismel bought the jewel from Lara.",
        ["3315"] = "Trader Lara's purchase records. It is recorded that Leopold of the Black Lion brought the jewel.",
        ["3316"] = "A portion of Leopold's Diary. It is recorded that 3 deserters died and became undead while escaping to the Wastelands.",
        ["3317"] = "Gem that can be obtained from Magister Iker. Find all 6 of Aklantoth gems and take them to Orim the Shadow.",
