        ["9568"] = "Dark elemental attack attribute increases by % when bestowed on a weapon. Holy elemental defense attribute increases by % when bestowed on an armor. Attribute Stones can be used up to attribute level 12. Additionally, a maximum of three types of elemental attribute can be bestowed on an armor. Opposite attributes cannot be bestowed together.",
        ["9569"] = "Holy elemental attack attribute increases by % when bestowed on a weapon. Dark elemental defense attribute increases by % when bestowed on an armor. Attribute Stones can be used up to attribute level 12. Additionally, a maximum of three types of elemental attribute can be bestowed on an armor. Opposite attributes cannot be bestowed together.",
        ["9570"] = "Red Crystal that absorbs souls, stage 14. Special abilities can be applied to the weapon when absorbing certain amount of souls. Every time it is used, it consumes 26 of MP. However, the Soul Crystal of this stage absorbs souls by itself, so there is no need for using the Soul Crystal to monsters.",
        ["9571"] = "Blue Crystal that absorbs souls, stage 14. Special abilities can be applied to the weapon when absorbing certain amount of souls. Every time it is used, it consumes 26 of MP. However, the Soul Crystal of this stage absorbs souls by itself, so there is no need for using the Soul Crystal to monsters.",
        ["9572"] = "Green Crystal that absorbs souls, stage 14. Special abilities can be applied to the weapon when absorbing certain amount of souls. Every time it is used, it consumes 26 of MP. However, the Soul Crystal of this stage absorbs souls by itself, so there is no need for using the Soul Crystal to monsters.",
