        ["13008"] = "Spellbook needed to learn Bless the Blood. Used by Shillien Elders.\\nRequired level: 40",
        ["13010"] = "Dimensional item\\nExtra entrance pass that lets you enter Kamaloka (Hall of the Abyss). Can cancel the limit on entrance if used while a limit on entrance to the Hall of the Abyss exists. Can only be used once a day outside the instant zone. After use, the effect disappears at the corresponding instant dungeon's reset time. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["13011"] = "Dimensional item\\nExtra entrance pass that lets you enter Near Kamaloka. Can cancel the limit on entrance if used while a limit on entrance to Near Kamaloka exists. Can only be used once a day outside the instant zone. After use, the effect disappears at the corresponding instant dungeon's reset time. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["13012"] = "Dimensional item\\nExtra entrance pass that lets you enter Kamaloka (Labyrinth of the Abyss). Can cancel the limit on entrance if used while a limit on entrance to the Labyrinth of the Abyss exists. Can only be used once a day outside the instant zone. After use, the effect disappears at the corresponding instant dungeon's reset time. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["13013"] = "Goods earmarked for Gesto. Collect 300 and take them to him.",
        ["13014"] = "Seal stamped on a freight chest. Take it to Gesto.",
        ["13015"] = "Dimensional item\\nIncreases by 3 slots the free teleport list, which can remember designated locations. Can expand up to 9 slots. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["13016"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that is consumed when moving to the remembered location. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["13017"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that allows you to summon a hunting helper who temporarily casts warrior-type battle support magic. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. ",
        ["13018"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that allows you to summon a hunting helper who temporarily casts magician-type battle support magic. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. ",
        ["13019"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that allows you to summon a warrior-type battle hunting helper. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. ",
        ["13020"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that allows you to summon a magician-type battle hunting helper. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. ",
        ["13021"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that allows you to change a character's name color. You can change back to the original name color by using the \"/resetname\" command after changing the name color. If there is no original name, the name will disappear. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["13027"] = "Dimensional item\\nGift Box that gives you an item once a day. Can be used for 30 days. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
