        ["13763"] = "Badge bearing the mark of Goddard territory.",
        ["13764"] = "Badge bearing the mark of Rune territory.",
        ["13765"] = "Badge bearing the mark of Schuttgart territory.",
        ["13766"] = "Certificate showing your qualification as a mercenary.",
        ["13767"] = "Certificate showing your qualification as a mercenary.",
        ["13768"] = "Certificate showing your qualification as a mercenary.",
        ["13769"] = "By putting catalyzer inside Seed of Infinity, the device creates artificial tissue to eliminate the monsters that attack the Seed of Life. Can be used only to defend the instant dungeon Hall of Erosion in the Seed of Infinity. Exclusively used by Dwarf Fighters, Artisans, Warsmiths, and Maestros. Cannot be exchanged or dropped.",
        ["13771"] = "It's an ointment that's made of the ingredients easily found in daily life and almost completely blocks the skin oxidation. It lessens the effects of lethal de-buff skills inside the Hall of Erosion. Can be used only inside Hall of Erosion instant dungeons.",
        ["13772"] = "A wondrous curative cloth that almost completely blocks the foreign contagion, which is the true nature of the Seed of Infinity, when you adhere it to your body. It increases Resistance to bleeding, poison, and Netherworld's Magyun induced special de-buff skills that the monsters use inside Seed of Infinity. Can be used only inside Seed of Infinity instant dungeons.",
        ["13773"] = "An ancient Gracian scent used to keep a body from decaying. It stops severe bleeding up to the maximum effect 8 caused by the monsters inside Seed of Infinity. Can be used only inside Seed of Infinity instant dungeons.",
        ["13774"] = "An ancient Gracian scent used to cure people who are possessed by ghosts. It neutralizes the powerful poison up to the maximum effect 8 caused by the monsters inside Seed of Infinity. Can be used only inside Seed of Infinity instant dungeons.",
        ["13775"] = "A wondrous drug that seems to have been used in ancient Gracian sacrificial rituals. It cancels the effect of bleeding and poison caused by the monsters inside Seed of Infinity up to the maximum effect 8 or Netherworld's Magyun induced special de-buff up to the maximum effect 4. Can be used only inside Seed of Infinity instant dungeons.",
        ["13776"] = "Amulet frequently used by ancient Gracian nobles. It gives the ability to resurrect and protection against death. Can be used only inside Seed of Infinity instant dungeons. Cannot be exchanged or dropped.",
        ["13777"] = "Lavishly adorned with jewels, this box looks like contains items of exceeding value.",
        ["13778"] = "Covered in opaque multi-colored mother-of-pearl, just looking at this box fills you with expectation.",
        ["13779"] = "Covered in gold, this box looks like it would fetch a hefty sum in any market.",
        ["13780"] = "Covered in silver, this box shines like a mirror.",
        ["13781"] = "This utilitarian box looks like it might contain some useful items.",
        ["13782"] = "This plain box makes you curious to look inside.",
        ["13783"] = "This small box can't hold anything of value -- can it?",
        ["13784"] = "This small, battered-looking box probably isn't worth your time.",
        ["13785"] = "This old, dust-covered box looks fairly worthless.",
        ["13786"] = "This box looks like it's falling apart.",
