        ["14055"] = "Dimensional item\\nReplenishes 100% Vitality upon use. Re-use time is 60 minutes. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed.Can be shared between characters within the same account through the Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["14061"] = "This whistle allows you to summon a Superior Minion who will support you during battle. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed.",
        ["14062"] = "This whistle allows you to summon a Superior Minion who will support you during battle. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed.",
        ["14063"] = "This whistle allows you to summon a Superior Minion who will support you during battle. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed.",
        ["14064"] = "This whistle allows you to summon a Superior Minion who will support you during battle. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed.",
        ["14065"] = "Dimensional item\\nAn exchange coupon that can be exchanged for a necklace that allows you to summon a High Quality Hunting Helper (5 hours). Can be exchanged through the Dimensional Merchant. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["14068"] = "Dimensional item\\nReplenishes Vitality 100% during use. Duration for reuse: 60 minutes. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["14074"] = "Dimensional item\\nAn exchange coupon that can be redeemed for a whistle that allows you to summon a Superior Minion for 5 hours. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["14078"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that raises a D-Grade weapon's enchant rate by 20%. Can only be used on items with 3~9 enchants. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["14079"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that raises a C-Grade weapon's enchant rate by 18%. Can only be used on items with 3~9 enchants. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["14080"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that raises a B-Grade weapon's enchant rate by 15%. Can only be used on items with 3~9 enchants. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["14081"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that raises an A-Grade weapon's enchant rate by 12%. Can only be used on items with 3~9 enchants. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["14082"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that raises an S-Grade weapon's enchant rate by 10%. Can only be used on items with 3~9 enchants. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["14083"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that raises a D-Grade armor's enchant rate by 35%. Can only be used on items with 3~9 enchants. For one-piece items, can only be used on items with 4~9 enchants. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["14084"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that raises a C-Grade armor's enchant rate by 27%. Can only be used on items with 3~9 enchants. For one-piece items, can only be used on items with 4~9 enchants. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["14085"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that raises a B-Grade armor's enchant rate by 23%. Can only be used on items with 3~9 enchants. For one-piece items, can only be used on items with 4~9 enchants. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["14086"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that raises an A-Grade armor's enchant rate by 18%. Can only be used on items with 3~9 enchants. For one-piece items, can only be used on items with 4~9 enchants. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
        ["14087"] = "Dimensional item\\nItem that raises an S-Grade weapon's enchant rate by 15%. Can only be used on items with 3~9 enchants. For one-piece items, can only be used on items with 4~9 enchants. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse. Can be shared between characters within the account through Dimensional Merchant.",
