        ["14765"] = "Entrance pass that lets you enter Near Kamaloka for a second time. Can cancel the limit on entrance if used while a limit on entrance to Rim Kamaloka exists. Can only be used once a day outside the instant zone. After use, the effect disappears at the corresponding instant dungeon's reset time. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed.",
        ["14766"] = "Candy basket for showing your heart on White Day. Contains 5 White Day candies. Can receive a bonus limited item  (coronet, suit, Agathion - Juju) occasionally. Cannot be dropped or destroyed. Cannot be registered at a private shop.",
        ["14767"] = "Candy basket for showing your heart on White Day. Contains 1 White Day candies. Can receive a bonus limited item  (Kat the Cat Hat, Agathion Seal Bracelet - Love) occasionally. Cannot be dropped or destroyed. Cannot be registered at a private shop.",
        ["14768"] = "White Day gift box for solo players. Contains 1 solo escape petition. Can receive a bonus limited item  (wild rose pig candy) occasionally. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Cannot be registered at a private shop.",
        ["14769"] = "White Day candy filled with a loving heart. Energy is fully replenished upon use. Duration for reuse: 60 minutes. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Cannot be registered at a private shop.",
        ["14770"] = "Fragrant grass that wishes for a solo player's escape. Energy is maintained for 10 minutes upon use. Re-use time is 30 minutes. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Cannot be registered at a private shop.",
