        ["15356"] = "A cocktail made of various rare fruits.  It has better effects than the Sweet Fruit Cocktail. When consumed, it bestows temporary effects of Might, Shield, Wind Walk, Focus, Death Whisper, Guidance, Bless Shield, Bless Body, Haste, and Vampiric Rage for 1h.",
