        ["15381"] = "July 7th event. Enchant scroll exclusively for the Weaver's Multi-colored Clothes. Increases the P. Def. and Magic M. Def. of the Weaver's Multi-colored Clothes. Can be safely enchanted to +3, and the item disappears when the enchant fails. When the Weaver's Multi-colored Clothes is enchanted above +4, attributes, STR, CON, INT, and MEN also increase according to the enhancement value. Can only be used during the July 7th event period, and it is deleted in bulk once the event ends.",
        ["15382"] = "Enchant scroll exclusively for the Vitality Belt. Increases the Vitality Belt's P. Def. and Magic M. Def. Vitality maintenance effect. Vitality maintenance re-use time reduced. Can be safely enchanted to +3, and the item disappears when the enchant fails. When the Vitality Belt is enchanted above +4, vitality maintenance duration increases, and the decreases vitality maintenance re-use time. Can only be used during the Vitality Belt event period, and it s deleted in bulk once the event ends.",
