        ["15492"] = "Sel Mahum salmon porridge. Smells better than expected… but not by much.",
        ["15493"] = "Pouch containing the spores of Fantasy Mushrooms, which grow in the Plains of the Lizardmen. Detailed information can be obtained from Investigator Sally on the Plains of the Lizardmen.",
