        ["15499"] = "Vial containing the blood of Tanta Lizardmen. Take it to Investigator Laki on the Plains of the Lizardmen.",
        ["15500"] = "Diary containing the daily life of the Sel Mahum. Take it back to Guard Stan of Oren Village.",
        ["15501"] = "Part of the cookbook used by the Sel Mahum Chef. Take it back to Guard Stan of Oren Village.",
