        ["17130"] = "A bouquet of freesias which implies innocent naivety. If used against a chaotic character or a character whose name is purple, your name will turn purple. Can also be used on Event Manager Freya in town.",
        ["17131"] = "A bouquet of gypsophila which implies sorrow. If used against a chaotic character or a character whose name is purple, your name will turn purple. Can also be used on Event Manager Freya in town.",
        ["17132"] = "A cocktail dedicated to the heroine of the play <Pink Lady> in a celebration of its success, which was first performed on the stage in London in 1912. If used against a chaotic character or a character whose name is purple, your name will turn purple. Can also be used on Event Manager Freya in town.",
        ["17133"] = "A cocktail with fresh color of summer green and sweet fragrance, which reminds of bugs flying from flower to flower following the scent in the month of June. If used against a chaotic character or a character whose name is purple, your name will turn purple. Can also be used on Event Manager Freya in town.",
        ["17134"] = "A gourmet cheesecake that is soft like a soufflé and delightfully sweet. If used against a chaotic character or a character whose name is purple, your name will turn purple. Can also be used on Event Manager Freya in town.",
        ["17135"] = "A freshly-baked baguette that is soft and delicious unlike its tough look. If used against a chaotic character or a character whose name is purple, your name will turn purple. Can also be used on Event Manager Freya in town.",
        ["17136"] = "A cream bun that features sweet and soft custard cream made of egg yolk, instead of normal butter cream or whipped cream. If used against a chaotic character or a character whose name is purple, your name will turn purple. Can also be used on Event Manager Freya in town.",
        ["17137"] = "A cute looking candy perfect for a gift. If used against a chaotic character or a character whose name is purple, your name will turn purple.",
        ["17138"] = "Gift box containing Freya's heart.",
        ["17139"] = "Scroll that changes your appearance into that of Anakim for 30 minutes. Cannot be traded, dropped, or stored in a private store. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["17140"] = "Scroll that changes your appearance into that of Zaken for 30 minutes. Cannot be traded, dropped, or stored in a private store. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["17158"] = "Increase Physical Attack by 15%, Magical Attack by 20%, and Speed by 10 for 10 minutes. ",
        ["17159"] = "Increase P. Critical Rate by 15, M. Critical Rate  by 2, and Speed by 10 for 10 minutes. Recovers 5% of the standard short-range physical damage inflicted on the enemy as HP.",
        ["17160"] = "Increase Max. Attack Speed by 20%, Casting Spd. by 20%, and Speed by 20 for 10 minutes.",
        ["17161"] = "The luckiest person will be given a special fortune box on April Fool's Day. What will be inside?",
        ["17162"] = "Shards obtained by hunting golems. Collect these and bring them to Yasheni.",
        ["17163"] = "When used, increases Max MP by 20%, MP recovery bonus by 20%, HP recovery bonus by 20%, Magic Critical Rate by 100%, Physical Critical power by 20%, P. Atk. by 10%, P. Def. by 20%, Atk. Spd. by 20%, M. Atk. by 20%, M. Def. by 20%, Casting Spd. by 20%, and resistance to debuffs by 10% for 1h. Also decreases Speed by 20% and skill MP consumption by 5%. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed.",
