        ["17225"] = "Key that opens the door to the Armory inside the Relic Safehouse of the Seal of the Saintess. You cannot enter the Armory without this key.",
        ["17226"] = "Rune mark created by magic for Elcadia's test. ",
        ["17227"] = "Rune token created by magic for Elcadia's test. ",
        ["17228"] = "One of the relics stored inside the Seal of the Saintess. This scroll emanates an unusual energy. The scroll is very old and worn. It must be handled with care.",
        ["17229"] = "One of the relics stored inside the Seal of the Saintess. This shield emanates an unusual energy. But it is very worn and large. It is fragile and cannot be used in battle.",
        ["17230"] = "One of the relics stored inside the Seal of the Saintess. The sword emanates an unusual energy. But it is very worn and large. It is fragile and cannot be used in battle.",
        ["17231"] = "One of the relics stored inside the Seal of the Saintess. This staff emanates an unusual energy. But it is very worn and heavy. It is fragile cannot be used in battle.",
        ["17232"] = "Wrapped pack containing a Ball Trapping Gnosian Agathion. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Cannot use a private store. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
