        ["17234"] = "Wrapped pack containing a Penalty Kick Agathion. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Cannot use a private store. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["17235"] = "Special gift in commemoration of the World Cup. Can obtain various items by using it.",
        ["17236"] = "Gift in commemoration of the World Cup victory. Can obtain Nevit's Hourglass and Voice by using it.",
        ["17237"] = "Gift in commemoration of the World Cup victory. Can obtain Nevit's Hourglass and Voice by using it.",
        ["17238"] = "Document that proves participation in the Olympiad Match 3. Take this document to the Olympiad Operator to receive the minimum reward.",
        ["17239"] = "Document that proves participation in the Olympiad Match 5. Take this document to the Olympiad Operator to receive an incomplete reward.",
        ["17240"] = "Document that proves participation in the Olympiad Match 10. Take this document to the Olympiad Operator to receive a whole reward.",
        ["17241"] = "Certificate that proves participation in the Olympiad team event 5 matches. Take the certificate to the Olympiad Operator. If you take it with the class-free and class battle certificates, you can expect a greater reward.",
        ["17242"] = "Certificate that proves participation in the Olympiad class-free battle 5 matches. Take the certificate to the Olympiad Operator. If you take it with the team event and class battle certificates, you can expect a greater reward.",
        ["17243"] = "Certificate that proves participation in the Olympiad class battle 5 matches. Take the certificate to the Olympiad Operator. If you take it with the team event and class-free battle certificates, you can expect a greater reward.",
        ["17244"] = "Document needed to confirm 2 consecutive wins in the Olympiad. Take this confirmation to the Olympiad Operator to receive the minimum reward.",
        ["17245"] = "Document needed to confirm 5 consecutive wins in the Olympiad. Take this document to the Olympiad Operator to receive an incomplete reward.",
        ["17246"] = "Document needed to confirm 10 consecutive wins in the Olympiad. Take this document to the Olympiad Operator to receive a whole reward.",
        ["17247"] = "Herb that brings Vitality to stage 4 for 10 minutes upon use. Effect works for all party members.",
        ["17248"] = "A summoning item, you can call a raid monster at a certain location in the Dragon Valley. But if the raid monster has already been summoned, it cannot be called.",
        ["17249"] = "Dragon Skull obtained after finishing off the raid monster that lives in the Dragon Valley. After obtaining the dragon skulls from all 7 different raid monsters, bring them to Gilmore.",
        ["17250"] = "Baby Dragon obtained after finishing off the raid monster that lives in the Dragon Valley. After obtaining the baby dragon, bring it to the separated soul in the Dragon Valley.",
        ["17251"] = "Drake Lord's essence. Bring it to Theodric.",
        ["17252"] = "Behemoth Leader's Essence. Bring it to Theodric.",
        ["17253"] = "Dragon Beast's Essence. Bring it to Theodric.",
        ["17254"] = "Old and tattered box. You can hear a rattling sound when you shake it.",
        ["17255"] = "When enchanted, P. Atk. increases by 4 for A-grade one-handed swords, one-handed blunts, daggers, spears, and other weapons. P. Atk. increases by 5 for two-handed swords, two-handed blunts, dualswords, and two-handed combat weapons. P. Atk. increases by 8 for bows. M. Atk. increases by 3 for all weapons. Starting at +4, P. Atk. / M. Atk. bonus double. Enchanting is safe up to +3. If enchanting fails, the item will not be crystallized but the enchant value will be reset to 0.",
        ["17256"] = "When enchanted, P. Def. increases by 1 for A-grade armor and accessories. Starting at +4, P. Def. increases by 3 and a HP bonus is granted. Enchanting is safe up to +3, but one-piece body armor can be safely enchanted up to +4. If enchanting fails, the item will not be crystallized but the enchant value will be reset to 0.",
        ["17257"] = "When enchanted, P. Atk. increases by 3 for B-grade one-handed swords, one-handed blunts, daggers, spears, and other weapons. P. Atk. increases by 4 for two-handed swords, two-handed blunts, dualswords, and two-handed combat weapons. P. Atk. increases by 6 for bows. M. Atk. increases by 3 for all weapons. Starting at +4, P. Atk. / M. Atk. bonus double. Enchanting is safe up to +3. If enchanting fails, the item will not be crystallized but the enchant value will be reset to 0.",
        ["17258"] = "When enchanted, P. Def. increases by 1 for B-grade armor and accessories. Starting at +4, P. Def. increases by 3 and a HP bonus is granted. Enchanting is safe up to +3, but one-piece body armor can be safely enchanted up to +4. If enchanting fails, the item will not be crystallized but the enchant value will be reset to 0.",
        ["17259"] = "When enchanted, P. Atk. increases by 3 for C-grade one-handed swords, one-handed blunts, daggers, spears, and other weapons. P. Atk. increases by 4 for two-handed swords, two-handed blunts, dualswords, and two-handed combat weapons. P. Atk. increases by 6 for bows. M. Atk. increases by 3 for all weapons. Starting at +4, P. Atk. / M. Atk. bonus double. Enchanting is safe up to +3. If enchanting fails, the item will not be crystallized but the enchant value will be reset to 0.",
        ["17260"] = "When enchanted, P. Def. increases by 1 for C-grade armor and accessories. Starting at +4, P. Def. increases by 3 and a HP bonus is granted. Enchanting is safe up to +3, but one-piece body armor can be safely enchanted up to +4. If enchanting fails, the item will not be crystallized but the enchant value will be reset to 0.",
        ["17261"] = "When enchanted, P. Atk. increases by 2 for all D-grade weapons with the exception of bow, which will increase by 4. M. Atk. increases by 2 for all weapons. Starting at +4, P. Atk. / M. Atk. bonus double. Enchanting is safe up to +3. If enchanting fails, the item will not be crystallized but the enchant value will be reset to 0.",
        ["17262"] = "When enchanted, P. Def. increases by 1 for D-grade armor and accessories. Starting at +4, P. Def. increases by 3 and a HP bonus is granted. Enchanting is safe up to +3, but one-piece body armor can be safely enchanted up to +4. If enchanting fails, the item will not be crystallized but the enchant value will be reset to 0.",
        ["17263"] = "When enchanted, P. Atk. increases by 5 for S-grade one-handed swords, one-handed blunts, daggers, spears, and other weapons. P. Atk. increases by 6 for two-handed swords, two-handed blunts, dualswords, and two-handed combat weapons. P. Atk. increases by 10 for bows. M. Atk. increases by 4 for all weapons. Starting at +4, P. Atk. / M. Atk. bonus double. Enchanting is safe up to +3. If enchanting fails, the item will not be crystallized but the enchant value will be reset to 0.",
        ["17264"] = "When enchanted, P. Def. increases by 1 for S-grade armor and accessories. Starting at +4, P. Def. increases by 3 and a HP bonus is granted. Enchanting is safe up to +3, but one-piece body armor can be safely enchanted up to +4. If enchanting fails, the item will not be crystallized but the enchant value will be reset to 0.",
        ["17265"] = "A certificate received from the Witness of Dawn Franz. It says that if you show this certificate to Priest Wood, he will exchange it for an occupation specific Forgotten Scroll that can be learned at level 81.",
        ["17266"] = "A command stone made by Antharas embedded in his high commanding minions so he will always have control over them. Used to create Antharas Blood Crystal. Bring it to a Separated Soul.",
        ["17267"] = "Small crystal particles made from the blood of Antharas. After his blood was spilt, the land absorbed the blood and acted as a filter that separated the poison from the blood creating a pure form of his blood that crystallized over time. Used to create an Atharas's Blood Crystal. Bring it to a Separated Soul.",
        ["17268"] = "Using the power held within the blood of Antharas, this crystal can revive and fully restore EXP of all dead characters in the Command Channel. Can only be used while inside the Lair of Antharas. Reuse time is 1 hour.",
        ["17272"] = "Special gift that commemorates the conquest of Dragon Valley. When used, you can obtain an Antharas Agathion seal bracelet.",
        ["17273"] = "Special gift that commemorates the completion of the Seven Sign quest. When used, you can obtain a Nevit's Messenger Kanna Agathion seal bracelet.",
        ["17274"] = "Special gift that commemorates the completion of the Seven Sign quest. When used, you can obtain a Guardian of the Dawn Kallesin Agathion seal bracelet.",
        ["17275"] = "Certificate that shows receipt of a Strider pet. You can exchange the exchange coupon for the Strider pet through the News Informer. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or put in private store. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["17276"] = "Scroll that replenishes 5,000,000 SP.",
        ["17277"] = "Scroll that replenishes 100,000,000 SP.",
        ["17278"] = "Dimensional item pack. Wrapped pack containing a Strider pet exchange coupon. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["17279"] = "Gift box containing 1 Anakim Transformation Scroll. When used, you can obtain a Transformation Scroll: Anakim. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed.",
