        ["17281"] = "Box that Isabel Silvershadow in Hunters Village asks you to deliver. Bring it to Valley Trader Kitzka in Dragon's Valley.",
        ["17282"] = "Dimensional Item Pack\\nGift box containing Nevit's Hourglass, Freya's Refreshing Breeze, and Ice Watermelon Hat. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["17283"] = "Dimensional item\\nHourglass that increases Nevit's blessing time by 4 hour(s). Can be used regardless of the level. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["17284"] = "Dimensional item\\nHourglass that increases Nevit's blessing time by 4 hour(s). Can be used regardless of the level. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["17285"] = "Dimensional item\\nWhen used, you can feel the Vitality recovery herb's effect for 4 hour(s). But there will be no effect when the \"Birthday Joy\" effect is applied. Re-use time is 60 minutes. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["17286"] = "Dimensional item\\nWhen used, you can feel the Vitality recovery herb's effect for 4 hour(s). But there will be no effect when the \"Birthday Joy\" effect is applied. Re-use time is 60 minutes. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["17287"] = "Dimensional Item Pack\\nGift box containing Nevit's Hourglass, Freya's Refreshing Breeze, and Ice Watermelon Hat. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
