        ["22005"] = "A Divine Armor Enchant Crystal and a high grade Ancient Armor Enchant Crystal can be acquired at a constant rate. Cannot be exchanged or dropped.",
        ["22006"] = "10 % increase in enchant success rate. \\nAttack power for D-grade sword, one-handed blunt, one-handed dagger, spear, other swords, two-handed sword, two-handed blunt, dualsword, and combat/two-handed weapons increases by 2 when enchanted. Attack power for bow weapons increases by 4. Magic power for all weapons increases by 2. Attack and magic power increase two times after +4. No exchange/drop are allowed.",
        ["22007"] = "10 % increase in enchant success rate. \\nAttack power for C-grade sword, one-handed blunt, one-handed dagger, spear, and other weapons increases by 3 when enchanted. Attack power for sword, two-handed blunt, two-handed dualsword, and combat and dual-handed weapons increases by 4. Attack power for bow weapons increases by 6. Magic power for all weapons increases by 3. Attack and magic power increase two times after +4. No exchange/drop available",
        ["22008"] = "10 % increase in enchant success rate. \\nAttack power for B-grade sword, one-handed blunt, one-handed dagger, spear, and other weapons increases by 3 when enchanted. Attack power for sword, two-handed blunt, two-handed dualsword, and combat and dual-handed weapons increases by 4. Attack power for bow weapons increases by 6. Magic power for all weapons increases by 3. Attack and magic power increase two times after +4. No exchange/drop available",
        ["22009"] = "10 % increase in enchant success rate. \\nAttack power for A-grade sword, one-handed blunt, one-handed dagger, spear, and other weapons increases by 4 when enchanted. Attack power for sword, two-handed blunt, two-handed dualsword, and combat and dual-handed weapons increases by 5. Attack power for bow weapons increases by 8. Magic power for all weapons increases by 3. Attack and magic power increase two times after +4. No exchange/drop available",
        ["22010"] = "10 % increase in enchant success rate. \\nDefense power for D-grade armor and accessories increases by 1. It increases by 3 after +4. It can safely be enchanted up to +3. For one-piece armor, it can safely be enchanted up to +4. No exchange/drop available",
        ["22011"] = "10 % increase in enchant success rate. \\nDefense power for C-grade armor and accessories increases by 1. It increases by 3 after +4. It can safely be enchanted up to +3. For one-piece armor, it can safely be enchanted up to +4. No exchange/drop available",
        ["22012"] = "10 % increase in enchant success rate. \\nDefense power for B-grade armor and accessories increases by 1. It increases by 3 after +4. It can safely be enchanted up to +3. For one-piece armor, it can safely be enchanted up to +4. No exchange/drop available",
        ["22013"] = "10 % increase in enchant success rate. \\nDefense power for A-grade armor and accessories increases by 1 and by 3 starting from +4. It can safely be enchanted up to +3. For one-piece armor, it can safely be enchanted up to +4. No exchange/drop available",
        ["22014"] = "10 % increase in enchant success rate. \\nWhen enchant fails, the existing enchant value is retained. \\nAttack power for B-grade sword, one-handed blunt, one-handed dagger, spear, and other weapons increases by 3 when enchanted. Attack power for sword, two-handed blunt, two-handed dualsword, and combat and dual-handed weapons increases by 4. Attack power for bow weapons increases by 6. Magic power for all weapons increases by 3. Attack and magic power increase two times after +4. Cannot use weapons enchanted by above 16. No exchange/drop available",
        ["22015"] = "10 % increase in enchant success rate. \\nWhen enchant fails, the existing enchant value is retained. \\nAttack power for A-grade sword, one-handed blunt, one-handed dagger, spear, and other weapons increases by 4 when enchanted. Attack power for sword, two-handed blunt, two-handed dualsword, and combat and dual-handed weapons increases by 5. Attack power for bow weapons increases by 8. Magic power for all weapons increases by 3. Attack and magic power increase two times after +4. Weapons enchanted by above 16 can be neither used, exchanged, nor dropped.",
        ["22016"] = "10 % increase in enchant success rate. \\nWhen enchant fails, the existing enchant value is retained. \\nDefense power for B-grade armor and accessories increases by 1. It increases by 3 after +4. It can safely be enchanted up to +3. For one-piece armor, it can safely be enchanted up to +4. Cannot use armor enchanted by above 16. No exchange/drop available",
        ["22017"] = "10 % increase in enchant success rate. \\nWhen enchant fails, the existing enchant value is retained. \\nDefense power for A-grade armor and accessories increases by 1 and by 3 starting from +4. It can safely be enchanted up to +3. For one-piece armor, it can safely be enchanted up to +4. Cannot use armor enchanted by above 16. No exchange/drop available",
        ["22018"] = "Enchant success rate is 100%. \\nAttack power for B-grade sword, one-handed blunt, one-handed dagger, spear, and other weapons increases by 3 when enchanted. Attack power for sword, two-handed blunt, two-handed dualsword, and combat and dual-handed weapons increases by 4. Attack power for bow weapons increases by 6. Magic power for all weapons increases by 3. Attack and magic power increase two times after +4. No exchange/drop available",
        ["22019"] = "Enchant success rate is 100%. \\nAttack power for A-grade sword, one-handed blunt, one-handed dagger, spear, and other weapons increases by 4 when enchanted. Attack power for sword, two-handed blunt, two-handed dualsword, and combat and dual-handed weapons increases by 5. Attack power for bow weapons increases by 8. Magic power for all weapons increases by 3. Attack and magic power increase two times after +4. No exchange/drop available",
        ["22020"] = "Enchant success rate is 100%. \\nDefense power for Grade C armor or accessory increases by 1 and by 3 starting from +4. It can safely be enchanted up to +3. For one-piece armor, it can safely be enchanted up to +4. No exchange/drop available",
