        ["20515"] = "A Divine Weapon Enchant Crystal and a high grade Ancient Weapon Enchant Crystal can be acquired at a constant rate. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or sold. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["20516"] = "A Divine Armor Enchant Crystal and a high grade Ancient Armor Enchant Crystal can be acquired at a constant rate. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or sold. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["20517"] = "10% increase in enchant success rate. \\nAttack power for S-grade sword, one-handed blunt, one-handed dagger, spear, and other weapons increases by 5 when enchanted. Attack power for sword, two-handed blunt, two-handed dualsword, and combat and dual-handed weapons increases by 6. Attack power for bow weapons increases by 10. Magic power for all weapons increases by 4. Attack and magic power increase two times after +4. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or sold. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["20518"] = "10% increase in enchant success rate. \\nDefense power for Grade S armor or accessory by 1 and by 3 starting from +4. It can be safely enchanted up to +3. For one-piece armor, it can be safely enchanted up to +4. Also increases HP according to level when armor is enchanted above +4. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or sold. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["20519"] = "10% increase in enchant success rate. \\nWhen enchant fails, the existing enchant value is retained. \\nAttack power for S-grade sword, one-handed blunt, one-handed dagger, spear, and other weapons increases by 5 when enchanted. Attack power for sword, two-handed blunt, two-handed dualsword, and combat and dual-handed weapons increases by 6. Attack power for bow weapons increases by 10. Magic power for all weapons increases by 4. Attack and magic power increase two times after +4. Cannot use weapons enchanted by above 16. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or sold. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["20520"] = "10% increase in enchant success rate. \\nWhen enchant fails, the existing enchant value is retained. \\nDefense power for Grade S armor or accessory by 1 and by 3 starting from +4. It can be safely enchanted up to +3. For one-piece armor, it can be safely enchanted up to +4. Also increases HP according to level when armor is enchanted above +4. Cannot use armors enchanted by above 16. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or sold. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
