        ["21579"] = "If you bring it to the Dimensional Merchant, you can exchange an ordinary S84 Grade item for a Masterwork Item.",
        ["21581"] = "Enchant scroll exclusive to Olf's T-shirt.\\nIncreases the T-shirt's P. Def. and M. Def. by 1. Starting from +4, increases P. Def. by 3. Can safely enchant to +3 and up to a max +10. From +4, \"basic abilities (CON, MEN, STR, INT, DEX, WIT)\" are raised in stages. Addtional options are added at +5, +7, +8 and +9. Cannot be dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21582"] = "Dimensional item\\nEnchant scroll exclusive to Olf's T-shirt.\\nIncreases the T-shirt's P. Def. and M. Def. by 1. Starting from +4, increases P. Def. by 3. Can safely enchant to +3 and up to a max +10. From +4, \"basic abilities (CON, MEN, STR, INT, DEX, WIT)\" are raised in stages. Additional options are added at +5, +7, +8 and +9. If the enchant fails, the existing enchant value becomes 0. Cannot be dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21584"] = "Dimensional item\\nGift box containing 1 Festival's Cloak - True Black. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21586"] = "Dimensional item\\nGift box containing 1 Festival's Cloak - True Black. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse. ",
        ["21589"] = "Dimensional item\\nGift box containing 1 Festival's Cloak - Pearl White. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse. ",
        ["21591"] = "Dimensional item\\nGift box containing 1 Festival's Cloak - Pearl White. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse. ",
        ["21592"] = "Dimensional item pack\\nGift box containing 1 each of Antharas's Earring (180 day), Valakas's Earring (180 day), Baium's Ring (180 day), Earring of Zaken (180 day), and Queen Ant's Ring (180 day). Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21593"] = "Shiny jewel obtained through the Wondrous Cubic. It looks like you would get quite a large sum by selling it at a shop.",
        ["21595"] = "Sweet and tasty birthday cake that you can share with others. This special cake casts a Vitality maintenance buff on all party members for 5 minutes - meaning that you will not lose Vitality while this buff is active. Your cake will disappear after 20 minutes. This item cannot be exchanged or dropped, but can be stored in your private warehouse.",
        ["21596"] = "Dimensional item\\nGift box containing 9 Vitality Replenishing Beverages and 6 feathers of blessing. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21597"] = "Dimensional item\\nGift box containing 9 Vitality Replenishing Beverages and 6 high quality hunting helpers. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21598"] = "Dimensional item\\nGift box containing 9 Vitality Replenishing Beverages and 3 feathers of blessing. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21599"] = "Dimensional item\\nGift box containing 9 Vitality Replenishing Beverages and 3 high quality hunting helpers. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21600"] = "Dimensional item\\nGift box containing 3 Vitality Replenishing Beverages, 3 feathers of blessing, and 3 high quality hunting helpers. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21700"] = "Dimensional item\\nGift box containing 1 Olf's T-shirt. Can be exchanged while in a pack. Cannot be dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21701"] = "Gift box containing 1 Olf's T-shirt. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21702"] = "Dimensional item\\nBlessed Olf's T-shirt Enchant Scroll. Gift box containig 1 each of the Large Firework and Honey Rice Cakes. Can be exchanged while in a pack. Cannot be dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21703"] = "Dimensional item\\nBlessed Olf's T-shirt Enchant Scroll. Gift box containig 6 each of the Large Firework and Honey Rice Cakes. Can be exchanged while in a pack. Cannot be dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21704"] = "Delicious honey rice cakes. When used, instantly recovers Max MP by 50%. Reuse time is 5 minutes. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21705"] = "Gift box containing 3 delicious honey rice cakes. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21707"] = "Dimensional item\\nEnchant scroll exclusive to Olf's T-shirt.\\nIncreases the T-shirt's P. Def. and M. Def. by 1. Starting from +4, increases P. Def. by 3. Can safely enchant to +3 and up to a max +10. From +4, \"basic abilities (CON, MEN, STR, INT, DEX, WIT)\" are raised in stages. Special skills are added at +5, +7, +8 and +9. If the enchant fails, the existing enchant value becomes 0. Cannot be dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21708"] = "Delicious honey rice cakes. When used, instantly recovers Max MP by 50%. Reuse time is 5 minutes. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21710"] = "When used, replenishes energy to 100%. Reuse time is 60 minutes. Cannot be destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21711"] = "When used, HP Recovery Bonus, Max MP, and Critical Atk. Rate +20%, and you can feel the effects of Prophecy of Water, Might, Haste, Empower, Acumen, Wind Walk, Vampiric Rage, Berserker Spirit, Shield, Focus, Death Whisper, Guidance, Clarity, Wild Magic, and Concentration for 1 hour. Cannot be destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21713"] = "When the seal is released, P. Def. and attribute resistance increase, and special skills can be used. It can be equipped only after releasing the seal through the weavers Olf Kanore in Aden or Olf Adams in Rune. Enchantment, attribute, and refining are impossible. Can be exchanged or dropped.",
        ["21714"] = "When the seal is released, P. Def. and attribute resistance increase, and special skills can be used. It can be equipped only after releasing the seal through the weavers Olf Kanore in Aden or Olf Adams in Rune. Enchantment, attribute, and refining are impossible. Can be exchanged or dropped.",
        ["21715"] = "When the seal is released, P. Def. and attribute resistance increase, and special skills can be used. It can be equipped only after releasing the seal through the weavers Olf Kanore in Aden or Olf Adams in Rune. Enchantment, attribute, and refining are impossible. Can be exchanged or dropped.",
        ["21722"] = "Small fragment that contains a part of Zaken's soul. See weaver Olf Adams to find out what use it has.",
        ["21723"] = "Small fragment that contains a part of Freya's soul. See weaver Olf Adams to find out what use it has.",
        ["21724"] = "Small fragment that contains a part of Frintezza's soul. See weaver Olf Adams to find out what use it has.",
        ["21725"] = "A severaly damaged staff piece. A mysterious light shines faintly.",
        ["21726"] = "When used, HP Recovery Bonus, Max MP, and Critical Atk. Rate +20%, and you can feel the effects of Prophecy of Water, Might, Haste, Empower, Acumen, Wind Walk, Vampiric Rage, Berserker Spirit, Shield, Focus, Death Whisper, Guidance, Clarity, Wild Magic, and Concentration for 1 hour. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21730"] = "7th Anniversary\\nLetter Collector's Gift. Upon use, for 2 hours, increases Atk. Spd. +15%, Casting Spd. +15%, Speed +20, and changes the appearance of the equipped weapon and armor to look like items from the past. Reuse time is 60 minutes.",
        ["21746"] = "Can open Treasure Chests between level 21-85 with 100% chance. When a character below level 77 uses it on a treasure chest that is more than 6 levels above, or when a character above level 78 uses it on a treasure chest that is more than 5 levels above, the key disappears but the reward cannot be obtained.",
        ["21747"] = "Treasure sack containing the treasure of beginner adventurers. Open it to obtain one random C or D-Grade Weapon.",
        ["21748"] = "Treasure sack containing the treasure of experienced adventurers. Open it to obtain one random B, A or S-Grade Weapon (Dynasty excluded).",
        ["21749"] = "Treasure sack containing the treasure of great adventurers. Open it to obtain one random Dynasty, Icarus or Vesper Weapon.",
        ["21750"] = "Token received by adventurers for their service to the Elmore king. If you bring it to Captain Mathias in Rune, you will receive a reward. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21751"] = "Jewelry box containing the precious treasure of Rune. When used, you can obtain 15 Crystals of Life with a certain rate of chance.",
        ["21752"] = "Jewelry box containing the precious treasure of Rune. When used, you can obtain a Talisman with a certain rate of chance.",
        ["21753"] = "Box containing the precious treasure of Elmore's renowned scholar Pablo. When used, you can obtain a hat with a certain rate of chance.",
