        ["21857"] = "Hero's Gold Chest\\nGift box containing 1 each of a Hero's Treasure Box, Dimensional Support Pack, Potion Support Pack, and Supplies Support Pack. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21858"] = "Wrapped pack containing 2 Superior Minion Coupons, 3 Feathers of Blessing, 5 Kamaloka (Hall of the Abyss, Labyrinth of the Abyss, Near) entrance passes, and 3 Vitality Replenishing Beverages. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed.",
        ["21859"] = "Wrapped pack containing 20 Greater Quick Healing Potions, 50 Greater Healing Potions, 5 Fresh Milks, and 5 Leaves of Appreciation. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed.",
        ["21860"] = "Wrapped pack containing 200,000 Mysterious Soulshots of all grade. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed.",
        ["21861"] = "When used, for 1 hour(s), energy is replenished when Exp. is acquired through hunting. Re-use time is 60 minutes. Can only be used at levels 1~75. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21862"] = "PC Vitality pack\\nGift box containing 3 PC Vitality. When used, has a chance of receiving a 1h~4h PC Vitality buff. Can only be used at levels 1~75. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21863"] = "When used, replenishes Vitality while hunting for all party members during 20 minutes. Re-use time is 60 minutes. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21864"] = "PC Blessing pack\\nGift box containing 1 PC Blessing. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21865"] = "When used, for 2 hour(s), energy is replenished when Exp. is acquired through hunting. Re-use time is 60 minutes. Can only be used at levels 1~75. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21866"] = "When used, for 3 hour(s), energy is replenished when Exp. is acquired through hunting. Re-use time is 60 minutes. Can only be used at levels 1~75. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21867"] = "When used, for 4 hour(s), energy is replenished when Exp. is acquired through hunting. Re-use time is 60 minutes. Can only be used at levels 1~75. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21868"] = "Gift provided for Halloween. When used, can obtain 20 Belldandy Summon Scrolls. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21869"] = "Hero's Gold Chest Pack\\nA gift box that contains a Hero's Gold Chest. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21871"] = "A coupon for an item set that helps a hero to grow stronger. Bestows an Equipment Set 7-Day Pak, a Button-Eyed Bear Doll Agathion 7-Day Pack, a Quick Healing Potion, and a Steam Beatle Mount Bracelet 7-Day Pack. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse. ",
        ["21872"] = "Herb that Rudolph likes. When the seal on Rudolph is removed, Rudolph automatically eats for 10 minutes.",
        ["21873"] = "Santa Claus's treasure box. When used, you can receive Santa Claus's gift.",
        ["21874"] = "Item for obtaining Fame. If you bring it to the Olympiad Manager, you can exchange it for 100 Fame points.",
        ["21875"] = "You can use this item if you have gathered 30 tree branches to start a campfire. A campfire near a battlefield can help to raise HP, MP, and CP recovery rate. You can only make campfires when you are away from towns. You can only receive the recovery bonus while near the campfire. \\nCannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21876"] = "Dimensional item\\nGift box containing 1 each of Pa'agrio's Warm Breeze - 4 hour pack, Nevit's Hourglass - 4 hour pack, party cake, and shiny party hat. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21877"] = "Dimensional item\\nGift box containing 1 each of Pa'agrio's Warm Breeze - 4 hour pack, Nevit's Hourglass - 4 hour pack, party cake, and shiny party hat. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or destroyed. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21878"] = "Dimensional item pack\\nGift box containing 15 Pa'agrio's warm breezes. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21879"] = "Dimensional pack\\nGift box containing 15 Nevit's Hourglasses - 4 hours. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21880"] = "Dimensional item\\nWhen used, you can feel the vitality recovery herb's effect for 4 hour(s). But there will be no effect when the \"Birthday Joy\" effect is applied. Re-use time is 60 minutes. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21881"] = "Dimensional item\\nSummons a party cake that maintains vitality for 20 minutes. It'll be effective only when summoned away at a certain distance from the town. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["21883"] = "(Not In Use)",
        ["21884"] = "(Not In Use)",
        ["21885"] = "Dimensional item pack\\nGift box containing 2 improved rose spirit exchange tickets. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be shared between characters within an account through the Dimensional Merchant. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
