        ["22176"] = "Scroll that summons an Angry Bunny. If you rid the bunny of it's anger you can acquire Apiga. (De-rageifying is only possible through Bunny Pacifier Juice or Extra Strength Bunny Pacifier Juice.)",
        ["22177"] = "Scroll that summons a Fearless Angry Bunny. Sometimes after a Fearless Angry Bunny has been calmed down it can sometimes becomes a Raging Bunny. (De-rageifying is only possible through Bunny Pacifier Juice or Extra Strength Bunny Pacifier Juice.)",
