        ["22179"] = "Scroll that summons a Large Fearless Angry Bunny. Sometimes after a Large Fearless Angry Bunny has been calmed down it can sometimes becomes a Large Raging Bunny. (De-rageifying is only possible through Bunny Pacifier Juice or Improved Bunny Pacifier Juice.)",
        ["22180"] = "An event pack that can be obtained once every 12 hours per account. If you double click it, you will obtain lure scrolls and bunny pacifier juices that are needed for the event. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
