        ["15310"] = "Einhasad's Sacred Sword given by the Emperor of Elmoreden Schneiman.",
        ["15313"] = "Player Commendation exlusive weapon equivalent to a Forgotten Blade. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive weapon enchant scrolls. Increase Critical Rate by 84 and increases damage inflicted during PvP. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
        ["15314"] = "Player Commendation exlusive weapon equivalent to a Basalt Battlehammer. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive weapon enchant scrolls. Increase Max HP by 25% and increases damage inflicted during PvP. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
        ["15315"] = "Player Commendation exlusive weapon equivalent to a Imperial Staff. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive weapon enchant scrolls. Increases MP Recovery Rate and increases damage inflicted during PvP. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
        ["15316"] = "Player Commendation exlusive weapon equivalent to a Angel Slayer. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive weapon enchant scrolls. P. Atk. increases by 265 during a critical attack and increases damage inflicted during PvP. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
        ["15317"] = "Player Commendation exlusive weapon equivalent to a Dragon Hunter. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive weapon enchant scrolls. Increases Healing power and increases damage inflicted during PvP. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
        ["15318"] = "Player Commendation exlusive weapon equivalent to a Saint Spear. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive weapon enchant scrolls. Increases Max HP by 25% and increases damage inflicted during PvP. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
        ["15319"] = "Player Commendation exlusive weapon equivalent to a Demon Splinter. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive weapon enchant scrolls. Increases Critical Rate by 80 and increases damage inflicted during PvP. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
        ["15320"] = "Player Commendation exlusive weapon equivalent to a Heaven's Divider. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive weapon enchant scrolls. Increases Critical Rate by 84 and increases damage inflicted during PvP. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
        ["15321"] = "Player Commendation exlusive weapon equivalent to a Arcana Mace. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive weapon enchant scrolls. Increases Casting Spd. by 61 and increases damage inflicted during PvP. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
        ["15322"] = "Player Commendation exlusive weapon equivalent to a Draconic Bow. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive weapon enchant scrolls. Increases Critical Rate by 88 and increases damage inflicted during PvP. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
        ["15323"] = "Kamael exclusive weapon.\\nPlayer Commendation exclusive weapon equivalent to a Laevateinn. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive Weapon Enchant Scrolls. Increases Atk. Spd. by 7% and damage inflicted during PvP. When enchanted to +4 or more, during a critical attack, it has a chance of increasing P. Atk., M. Atk. and healing power, as well as decreasing MP consumption for skill use for you and your party members during a critical attack. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
        ["15324"] = "Kamael exclusive weapon.\\nPlayer Commendation exclusive weapon equivalent to a Gram. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive Weapon Enchant Scrolls. Increases Critical Rate by 84 and damage inflicted during PvP. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
        ["15325"] = "Kamael exclusive weapon.\\nPlayer Commendation weapon equivalent to a Sarunga. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive Weapon Enchant Scrolls. Increases Critical Rate by 88 and damage inflicted during PvP. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
        ["15326"] = "Player Commendation exlusive weapon equivalent to a Tallum Blade*Dark Legion's Edge. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive weapon enchant scrolls, and if enchanted to +4 or more, Max HP and Max CP increase by 15% and 30% respectively, and the damage inflicted during PvP increases. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
        ["15342"] = "Dimensional item\\nTransformation stick that turns you into a Aqua Elf Can be used for 60 days. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["15344"] = "Dimensional item\\nTransformation stick that turns you into a Aqua Elf Can be used for 60 days. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse.",
        ["15403"] = "Player Commendation exclusive weapon equivalent to a Berserker Blade. Can be enchanted with PC exclusive Weapon Enchant Scrolls. Increases Critical Rate by 73. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, or crystallized. Cannot be granted additional functions.",
