        ["16145"] = "Masterwork Item that increases Critical Rate. Kamael Exclusive Weapon: Vesper Cutter Conversion\\nHaste, Focus, or Health can be bestowed.\\nWhen enchanted to 4 or more, there is a chance that party members including yourself will get increased P. Atk., M. Atk. and the amount of recieved heal, and decreased MP consumption per skill during a critical attack. Increases damage inflicted during PvP. Improves the chance of CP recovery during an attack.",
